comment: Tucker (PHO) sets the screen on Ariza (HOU) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Howard (HOU) makes contact with the ball but also Goodwin's (PHO) arm and affects his driving layup attempt.
Goodwin (PHO) and Beverley (HOU) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Goodwin (PHO) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Beverley's (HOU) drive to the basket. Any contact on the play is initiated by Beverley.
Beverley (HOU) and Booker (PHO) make incidental contact with one another while reaching for the loose ball.
RHH shows that Tucker (PHO) steps OOB while in possession of the ball.
Beverley (HOU) does not establish a legal guarding position at the time of the contact with Goodwin (PHO).
RATR and R-SLA show that Beverley (HOU) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact that does not affect Goodwin's (PHO) layup attempt.
Chandler (PHO) commits a take foul on Beverley (HOU).
Ariza (HOU) cleanly knocks the ball away from Morris (PHO) on the inbound pass and any contact is incidental.
